 &UR; MAIN SPOT NEWS:
	   WASHINGTON _ Forced by prosecutors and political reality to
reverse course after seven months of denials, President Bill
Clinton prepares to tell a grand jury _ and possibly the world _
that he had an inappropriate relationship with volunteer Monica
Lewinsky. US-CLINTON-INVESTIGATION. Urgent series moving now with
testimony under way. By John Solomon. AP Photos WX102-110.
