Northern Ireland's worst terrorist attack. NIRELAND. Lead expected
by 1900 GMT. By Shawn Pogatchnik. AP Photos LON110, XOGH109-110,
XOMG106.
	   AUGHER, Northern Ireland _ One minute, they were shopping on a
Saturday afternoon like any other. The next minute, three
generations of a family were gone. Townspeople say it was family
that mattered most to Avril Monahan, pregnant with twins, and it
was family she died with _ her 18-month-old daughter and her
65-year-old mother. NIRELAND-ONE FAMILY. Expected by 1900 GMT. By
Kristin Gazlay.
	   KINSHASA, Congo _ Traipsing from Cuba to southern Congo and
neighboring Angola, President Laurent Kabila mounts a last-minute
drive to find support for his embattled government, and heads back
to his stronghold of Lubumbashi on Monday. In Kinshasa, tension
mounts amid another power outage. CONGO. Lead expected by 1900 GMT.
By Ian Stewart. AP Photos KIN101-104.
