<SLUG> BC-AP-Weekly News Calendar,0234 </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
Tuesday, August 18:
</HEADLINE>

<TEXT>
	   Berlin _ Berlin city government debates Holocaust memorial
finalists.
	   Berlin _ A second doping trial opens against three coaches and
two doctors from another former East Berlin women's swimming team.
