<TEXT>
	   TOKYO (AP) _ The U.S. dollar was trading at 146.09 yen on the
Tokyo foreign exchange market at 9 a.m. (0000 GMT) Tuesday, down
0.36 yen from its level of 146.45 as of 5 p.m. (0800 GMT) Monday.
