	   PEBBLE BEACH, California (AP) _ Final scores Monday from the
dlrs 2.5 million PGA Pebble Beach National Pro-Am, played on three
courses, all par-72: the 6,799-yard (6,187-meter) Pebble Beach Golf
Links, the 6,810-yard (6,197-meter) Spyglass Hill Golf Club and the
6,825-yard (6,210-meter) Poppy Hills Golf Club.
